Package EventListeners

This package provides the eventListener interfaces. Those interfaces are used to transmit events such as changeDialog or run URL to other classes, mainly to our main controller BrowsrController.
  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    ActionListener
    Interface that implements the clickButton method for the EventListener class.
    AddBookmarkListener
    Interface that implements the addBookmark method for the EventListener class.
    AdjustmentListener
    Interface that implements the elementChanged, elementChangedAndReset and the elementIncreased methods for the EventListener class.
    ChangeDialogListener
    Interface that implements the changeDialog method for the EventListener class.
    EventListener
    Main class of the EventListener classes.
    FormListener
    Interface that implements the handleFormSubmit method for the EventListener class.
    HyperLinkListener
    Interface that implements the run URL methods for the EventListener class.
    ReloadListener
    Interface that implements the redraw method for the EventListener class.
    SavePageListener
    Interface that implements the savePage method for the EventListener class.
    ScrollBarListener
    Interface that implements the scrollbarMoved method for the EventListener class.
    SearchBarListener
    Interface that implements the searchBarLoseFocus method for the EventListener class.
    SeparatorBarMoveListener
    Interface that implements the barMoved method for the EventListener class.
